                <para styleclass="Parameter-Header"><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">X-axis</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> : move the </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">active Blend-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> along the X-axis - so that it become earlier or later.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table"><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Element-Header" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor</text><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true"> does not (usually) change the </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Motion-Width" styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">Motion-Width</link><text styleclass="Body Table" translate="true">.</text></para>
